Use alembic commands from this directory:

- Generate initial migration:
  DB_URL=postgresql+psycopg2://postgres:postgres@localhost:5434/taxi alembic revision --autogenerate -m "init"
- Apply:
  DB_URL=postgresql+psycopg2://postgres:postgres@localhost:5434/taxi alembic upgrade head

Guidelines
- One change per migration; review autogenerate output
- Use staging before production; have rollback plan

